title: Baker Ross FN091 Shop Sticker Scenes - Pack of 5, Self-Adhesive Stickers for Kids, Crafts for Kids, Stickers for Children

features: Arts and Crafts for Kids: Kids can create their own shop scene decorated with these repositionable stickers! With over 30 stickers to choose from kids will love sticking and changing up their pictures!
Travel Activities for Kids: These sticker scenes are ideal for children to complete whilst travelling, or as party bag fillers for kids' birthday parties
Stickers for Kids: Kids can simply peel and stick the stickers into their desired positions on the background scene. Stickers are repositionable, so scenes can be changed and mixed up easily
Included in the Pack: This pack contains 5 sticker scenes. Each kit includes 5 printed card scenes (27cm x 18cm) and 30+ repositionable stickers per scene.

Made by Experts: Baker Ross has been designing and providing the very best art and craft supplies, and toys to schools, groups and parents for over 40 years. All products conform to General Product Safety Regulations, and state age recommendation where applicable.
description: From the manufacturer Immerse young entrepreneurs in the world of retail with Baker Ross's exciting shop-themed crafts. Foster creativity and role-play with the Wood Craft Cash Register Kit, allowing children to build their own register for imaginative store scenarios. Encourage artistic expression with 3D Colour-in Supermarket Shop Items, where kids can personalize and assemble their own shop essentials. Create a dynamic shopping experience with the Woodcraft Shop Display Kit, providing a platform for showcasing crafts and products. Let imaginations run wild with Shop Sticker Scenes, offering five scenes for decorating and storytelling. Enhance the shopping adventure with Push Along Sweet Cart Kit and Display Pick & Mix Stand Kit, inspiring pretend play and entrepreneurial spirit. With Baker Ross's shop-themed crafts, children can embark on exciting retail adventures, exercising creativity and imagination while having endless fun. Whether setting up a sweet cart, arranging products on display, or creating colorful sticker scenes, each activity offers a world of possibilities for play and exploration.
